# Build Outputs and Artifacts

## Build Directories
The following directories contain build outputs and should not be committed to version control:

```
node-library/
├── cjs/        # CommonJS build output
├── esm/        # ES Modules build output
├── tslib/      # TypeScript build output
└── coverage/   # Test coverage reports

storybook/
└── storybook-static/  # Built Storybook site
```

## Build Configuration
Build outputs are configured through several files:

### Node Library Builds
- [packages/node-library/.size-limit.json](mdc:/packages/node-library/.size-limit.json) - Bundle size limits
- [packages/node-library/.depcheckrc.yml](mdc:/packages/node-library/.depcheckrc.yml) - Dependency checking
- Build-specific TypeScript configs:
  - [packages/node-library/tsconfig.cjs.json](mdc:/packages/node-library/tsconfig.cjs.json)
  - [packages/node-library/tsconfig.esm.json](mdc:/packages/node-library/tsconfig.esm.json)
  - [packages/node-library/tsconfig.tslib.json](mdc:/packages/node-library/tsconfig.tslib.json)

### Build Cache
- `.turbo/` directories contain Turborepo build caches
- Build artifacts are tracked in various `.tsbuildinfo` files

## Ignored Files
Build outputs and artifacts are excluded from version control as specified in:
- [.gitignore](mdc:/.gitignore) - Root gitignore
- [packages/node-library/.gitignore](mdc:/packages/node-library/.gitignore) - Node library specific ignores
